---
import BannerImg from "../assets/images/banner.png";
---

<header
  class="container px-6 mx-auto py-10 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-between md:pt-24 lg:pt-32"
>
  <div class="lg:w-1/2">
    <div class="w-full space-y-6">
      <h1 class="w-4/4 md:w-2/3 text-5xl md:text-6xl font-medium">
        Impulsa tu negocio al siguiente nivel
      </h1>
      <p class="w-5/6 md:w-4/9">
        Creamos experiencias digitales que conectan con tu audiencia: desarrollo
        web y mobile atractivo, contenido estratégico y campañas de marketing
        que posicionan tu negocio donde debe estar.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
        <button
          class="px-[15px] py-[10px] md:px-[22px] md:py-[15px] font-medium bg-[#65fd08] rounded-md text-black cursor-pointer whitespace-nowrap border border-[#65fd08] hover:bg-white hover:text-dark duration-300"
        >
          Comenzar ahora
        </button>
        <button
          class="px-[15px] py-[10px] md:px-[22px] md:py-[15px] font-medium rounded-md bg-white text-black cursor-pointer whitespace-nowrap border border-black hover:bg-black hover:text-white duration-300"
        >
          Agenda tu consulta
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class='lg:w-1/2"' data-aos="fade-left">
    <div class="image">
      <img
        alt="Illustration"
        class="w-full h-auto mt-12 md:mt"
        src={BannerImg.src}
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
